South Africa May Retail Sales Growth Slowed to 10%, Liaison Committee Says

-- B y   A n a   M o n t e i r o
-- 
2011-06-22T14:32:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-22/south-africa-may-retail-sales-growth-slowed-to-10-liaison-committee-says.html
South African retail sales growth
slowed to 10 percent in May, the Retailer Liaison Committee, an
industry group, said in an e-mailed statement today.  Growth decelerated from 10.2 percent in April.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ana Monteiro at 
